      "updatedAt": 1717200000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• settings.json MERGED (+ .bak backup): agent teams ON, MEMORY_VAULT, in-process, 2 hooks\n• copies 4 agents -> ~/.claude/agents  (replaces {{MEM}} with the real path)\n• copies runtime -> ~/.claude/memory-team (lib.mjs, memory.mjs, hooks)\n• injects Memory Protocol into ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md\n• creates the central vault (default ~/.claude/memory-vault)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• settings.json MERGED (+ .bak backup): agent teams ON, MEMORY_VAULT, in-process, 2 hooks\n• copies 4 agents -> ~/.claude/agents  (replaces {{MEM}} with the real path)\n• copies runtime -> ~/.claude/memory-team (lib.mjs, memory.mjs, hooks)\n• injects Memory Protocol into ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md\n• creates the central vault (default ~/.claude/memory-vault)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
